A</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%A7m/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Qu%C3%A2n-minh-th%E1%BA%A7n-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-qObqKfTxo1mVHK33tZo-Zg">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Quân minh thần lương” - 奉和御製君明臣良</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%A7m/author-Muj2OcCc0igEuwPs2t2W-g">Ngô Thầm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Tr%E1%BA%A5n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-quy-t%C4%83ng-IV/poem-U1jHLBwTbdd9VEFbRmassA">Trấn Quốc quy tăng (IV) - 鎮國歸僧（IV）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-NP_3GqUI1Xnyh9_2fxbW-A">Vịnh nguyệt - 詠月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
